{"tid":1638940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣/口宣］林鄭黨鐵合謀懲罰市民支持反修例運動","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T15:19:34.000Z","uid":194298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6a45fd0541fe91181b0d2eca07a81c034228cb","tid":1638940,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:56:12.000Z","msg":"今日交通情況唔駛講，封左三日鐵令市民有假放不得都算<br />\n明明無壞可以正常通車，但就為左收錢迫市民排長龍入閘，公共運輸搵錢至上<br />\n8點收車另類宵禁，個個趕返屋企驚無車搭<br />\n<br />\n一定要將責任推返去政府身上，今日全日大混亂都係政府合謀黨鐵玩市民一獲<br />\n你支持暴徒丫ma，抵你死啦<br />\n你唔支持暴徒呀，又唔出黎反對佢地？<br />\n<br />\n總之就係用行政手段同所有正反市民作對<br />\n所謂損壞根本係少數不足以令黨鐵停駛三日<br />\n<br />\n依筆帳全港市民都一定要同林鄭黨鐵算清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec3687d92b4922eb0a37b613b6b00ad045e43b7","tid":1638940,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"推!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef47dba9b3aea36e3f44910c9e2011388b7f3816","tid":1638940,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"推爆佢，行動派做文宣，文靜派坐車用口宣<br />\n要幾矛頭直指林鄭"},{"pid":"1416320323d2a12be739f3260104d796df6407d7","tid":1638940,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6954f4e9f41238e85711c88d2e6482560d1f16a1","tid":1638940,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"275340d8915f41f8b02b2f24fa9ecf191ed3c29e","tid":1638940,"uid":125619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"723290b3b2f95a170b471a0e7d348551a3bc04b8","tid":1638940,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"大家開工啦<br />\n［圍觀師第一次出動］今晚去黨鐵站 （文宣好機會）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637519\" data-auto-link